---Create a Store Database




/**Mary's Interiors:
Vases (20)
Pillows (15)
Rugs (100)
Lamps (150)
Plants (10)
Tables (200)
Sofas (400)
Chairs (300)
Decor (110)
Shelves (130)
Storage Units (350)
Wall Art (100)
Mirrors (120)
Candles (5)
Cabinets (500)
**/
CREATE TABLE merchandise (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, name TEXT, price INTEGER, quanity INTEGER, aisle INTEGER, delivery INTEGER );


INSERT INTO merchandise VALUES (1, "Vases", 20, 60, 1, 0 );
